<newsItemPage guid="fe6cd0ee-a404-475d-997a-6275cb8fc841" id="48001" nodeName="Inghams Launches Digital Interactive Brochure for Winter 20/21 Ski Season" isDoc="" updated="2021-02-11T17:05:00.9730000Z" parentGUID="1b7d0072-ed7b-4662-bc79-9f228227818a" nodeTypeAlias="newsItemPage" templateAlias="NewsItemPage" sortOrder="0" published="false" isBlueprint="false">
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><strong>Skiers and snowboarders will be pleased to know that Inghams are cementing the news that the mountains will be open this coming season, with the launch of their <a rel="noopener" href="https://issuu.com/hotelplan2/docs/inghams_ski_2020_hr?fr=sN2VhZDQ1MDg" target="_blank" title="Brochure" data-anchor="?fr=sN2VhZDQ1MDg">winter 20/21 interactive brochure.</a></strong></p>
<p>Planning for the next Inghams’ mountain adventure can now be completed entirely online, as the ski holiday specialist continue to take bookings for the 20/21 winter season with the help of their new interactive brochure. Adding new destinations to their offering and focusing on the places skiers and snowboarders love the most, the tour operator will now be helping their customers follow the snow to 77 resorts, across 8 countries.</p>
<p>In preparation for this coming winter, Inghams have put over 85 years of experience into designing a brochure to suit their customers. Complete with hints and tips, alongside carefully chosen flights, resorts and accommodation the interactive brochure is the perfect tool for those dreaming of a family ski holiday, mind-blowing views or an off-piste adventure. Featuring handpicked destinations that deliver the choice, facilities and on-slope experiences Inghams’ customers expect—whilst helping to keep everyone safe.</p>
<p><strong>In a statement from Inghams, Paul Carter, CEO said:</strong></p>
<p>“Following lockdown, we know people are really looking forward to a well-deserved break in the mountains. With our offering for the 20/21 ski season collated into an interactive digital brochure, we’ll be saving paper and making it as easy as we can for our customers to get something in the diary to look forward to.</p>
<p>We hope our winter ski season programme, alongside our In Safe Hands campaign, and our continual endeavour to do the right thing enables our customers to travel with confidence. Essentially, we would like skiers and snowboarders to feel they can start getting excited about hitting the slopes again.”</p>
<p>Travelling from 15 different local departure airports, Inghams are including chalets and chalet hotels as well as a wide range of hotels and apartments across <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" target="_blank" title="France">France</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" target="_blank" title="Austria">Austria</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" target="_blank" title="Italy">Italy</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" target="_blank" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" target="_blank" title="Canada">Canada</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Andorra</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/516b1a33fc1149b9950be89be59e4816" href="/{localLink:umb://document/516b1a33fc1149b9950be89be59e4816}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a> and<a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" target="_blank" title="Lapland/Finland"> Lapland</a> in their 20/21 winter ski season brochure.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/d1b25faa2e9640028bb897b344b3d2d8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d1b25faa2e9640028bb897b344b3d2d8}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Parc Victoria">Hotel Parc Victoria in Cortina D-Ampezzo</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/e48c88a63722429b828e704ccf861c5e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e48c88a63722429b828e704ccf861c5e}" target="_blank" title="Pension Angelo (Corvara)">Pension Angelo in Corvara</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/ff8268653e81451ab76791f9d62d9a2b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ff8268653e81451ab76791f9d62d9a2b}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Mareo">Hotel Mareo in Plan de Corones</a>, and <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/84b905b8ed224af0b62dc2a5b4746327" href="/{localLink:umb://document/84b905b8ed224af0b62dc2a5b4746327}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Hermitage">Hotel Hermitage in Sauze d'Oulx</a> have been added to Inghams’ Italian selection of hotels, chalets and chalet hotels. In Austria, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/12cb1dd201c0496f9a3650d30816a0fa" href="/{localLink:umb://document/12cb1dd201c0496f9a3650d30816a0fa}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Alpine Palace">Hotel Alpine Palace</a> and <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/380ac586ffc4411b90570158669df974" href="/{localLink:umb://document/380ac586ffc4411b90570158669df974}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Der Gollinger">Hotel Gollinger in Hinterglemm</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/7f01587262c148e583c9fc8cd2dbb35d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f01587262c148e583c9fc8cd2dbb35d}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Bauer">Hotel Bauer</a> and <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/34540c874ddf4001a6ca52ef2354fb62" href="/{localLink:umb://document/34540c874ddf4001a6ca52ef2354fb62}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Kendler">Hotel Kendler in Saalbach</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/70646aa43ee24e4ca85ad3b54d6f62d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/70646aa43ee24e4ca85ad3b54d6f62d5}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Lebzelter">Hotel Lebzelter in Zell am See</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/12d3c604db094bd999cfc17d41a49eaf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/12d3c604db094bd999cfc17d41a49eaf}" title="Pension Martinshof">Hotel Martinshof in Obergurgl</a>, <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/b4226325d8e64d95a53c7d1959b9cff2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b4226325d8e64d95a53c7d1959b9cff2}" target="_blank" title="Tirol Lodge">Hotel Tirol Lodge in Ellmau</a>, and <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/2fc82c1647794c1ebd0412904f61c9f5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2fc82c1647794c1ebd0412904f61c9f5}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Kitzhof">Hotel Kitzhof in Kitzbuhel</a> have been added to the portfolio.</p>
<p>The launch of Inghams 20/21 winter contribution, includes a number of incentives for starting to think about where to ski this coming season. Including <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/3566891a2b9142d4afe57ea30f084428" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3566891a2b9142d4afe57ea30f084428}" target="_blank" title="Ski Hire Offer">50% off equipment hire or carriage when customers pre-book their lift pass</a> with Inghams and low booking deposits. Winter 20/21 ski holidays can be reserved for as little as £150pp, or £180pp for Canada, when booked before the end of September*.</p>
<p>These great offers teamed with Inghams’ reassurances that their customer’s money is safe, and the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/about-us/in-safe-hands" target="_blank" title="In safe hands">list of ways the tour operator plans to help keep everyone as safe as possible post COVID-19</a>, are fundamental to providing customers with that extra piece of mind.</p>
<p>In addition, Inghams’ ongoing partnership with Huski, the food and drink delivery service ideal for those staying in self-catering apartments, adds further reassurance for those unsure about eating-out following COVID-19. With Huski, holidaymakers can enjoy premium oven ready meals delivered to their door.</p>
<p><strong>And finally, Inghams customers can also make the most of the following <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/e424c795881c418eb4d77ec47a6a4912" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e424c795881c418eb4d77ec47a6a4912}" target="_blank" title="Exclusive Special Offers">exclusive discounts</a> and partner deals this coming winter.</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>15% off Snow &amp; Rock Clothing.</li>
<li>15% off Planks Clothing.</li>
<li>10% off Crevasse Clothing.</li>
<li>A pre-booking offer with APH to save up to 35% on the cost of airport parking.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><em>*The final balance is due 10 weeks before departure. For some dates there might be an increase to the deposit if the holiday includes a scheduled flight rather than a charter.</em></p>
<p><strong><em> Terms &amp; conditions apply. Subject to<span> availability.</span></em></strong><em><br /><br /></em></p>
<p><strong>-ENDS-</strong></p>
<p><strong>Company Information</strong></p>
<p>Inghams was founded by Walter Ingham in 1934, born out of his enduring passion for ski, mountaineering and walking.</p>
<p>Inghams recently celebrated its 85th year in business and the brand continues to pride itself on being one of the UK's leading, most experienced specialist tour operators, delivering a wide range of award-winning holidays to its loyal guests.</p>
<p>Today, Inghams offers ski holidays in the winter to 77 resorts in 8 countries, plus winter wonderland and Santa Breaks to Lapland, with flights from 15 UK regional airports. It also has a popular Summer Experiences holiday programme to many European destinations &amp; Canada, and a dedicated Self-guided and Escorted Tours programme. For more information, visit <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/">www.inghams.co.uk</a>. </p>
